        <updateDate>2021-07-28T16:10:35Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Fighting Oppression until the Reign of Castro Ends Act or the FORCE Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits removing Cuba from the list of state sponsors of terrorism until the President makes the determination that a transition government in Cuba is in power. Further, the President must submit a report that identifies terrorists and fugitives being provided safe haven in Cuba.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
